{"tid":2074474,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【保就業計劃】僱主名單出爐！優品360獲近1,600萬補貼,名創優品受惠員工310名","createTime":"2020-06-22T06:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T02:20:55.000Z","uid":11148,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8e7940f6a103934750eb8f7e03d02e9a8a7f1643","tid":2074474,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"據名單，<span style=\"color: red;\">養和醫療集團獲最多「保就業」計劃第一期的工資補貼，涉8,594萬元</span>。優品360（2360）旗下彩鷗國際有限公司獲1,596.5萬元資助，所得金額為第6位多，相比截至去年9月底半年純利1,346萬元還要多。其承諾受薪員工人數為680人；被指品牌LOGO抄襲日牌UNIQLO的內地品牌名創優品(MINISO)亦有申請，獲資助463.1萬元，承諾受薪員工人數310人。<br />\n<br />\n多間知名企業及上市公司均「榜上有名」，剛完成私有化的利豐（494）旗下利豐物流(香港)有限公司、利豐貨運（香港）及利豐物流管理，合共獲得資助金額2054.7萬元，承諾受薪員工人數共724人；周大福企業獲資助166.2萬元，承諾聘用人數63人；澳優乳業（1717）取得10.8萬元資助；嘉里系旗下嘉里物流聯網（636）及嘉里貨運分別獲48.6萬元及506.6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">優品360（2360）所獲資助比半年純利還要多。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200622/BYRKC23SAASQTAD2BSFHS4CKAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200622%2FBYRKC23SAASQTAD2BSFHS4CKAE%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=811c743e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200622%2FBYRKC23SAASQTAD2BSFHS4CKAE%2F&h=3c3bc0a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200622/BYRKC23SAASQTAD2BSFHS4CKAE/</a>"},{"pid":"e865eead3fad6f0b55eb55343e2eee350332a5cc","tid":2074474,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:44:06.000Z","msg":"養和有咁多人？<br />\n<br />\n美心呢？"},{"pid":"15ffc8325c41680215e3e1b922db765556780845","tid":2074474,"uid":156573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e7940f6a103934750eb8f7e03d02e9a8a7f1643","tid":2074474,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T06:35:18.000Z","msg":"據名單，<span style=\"color: red;\">養和醫療集團獲最多「保就業」計劃第一期的工資補貼，涉8,594萬元</span>。優品360（2360）旗下彩鷗國際有限公司獲1,596.5萬元資助，所得金額為第6位多，相比截至去年9月底半年純利1,346萬元還要多。其承諾受薪員工人數為680人；被指品牌LOGO抄襲日牌UNIQLO的內地品牌名創優品(MINISO)亦有申請，獲資助463.1萬元，承諾受薪員工人數310人。<br />\n<br />\n多間知名企業及上市公司均「榜上有名」，剛完成私有化的利豐（494）旗下利豐物流(香港)有限公司、利豐貨運（香港）及利豐物流管理，合共獲得資助金額2054.7萬元，承諾受薪員工人數共724人；周大福企業獲資助166.2萬元，承諾聘用人數63人；澳優乳業（1717）取得10.8萬元資助；嘉里系旗下嘉里物流聯網（636）及嘉里貨運分別獲48.6萬元及506.6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">優品360（2360）所獲資助比半年純利還要多。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200622/BYRKC23SAASQTAD2BSFHS4CKAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200622%2FBYRKC23SAASQTAD2BSFHS4CKAE%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=811c743e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200622%2FBYRKC23SAASQTAD2BSFHS4CKAE%2F&h=3c3bc0a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200622/BYRKC23SAASQTAD2BSFHS4CKAE/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T07:03:12.000Z","msg":"tvb都7百幾萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ccca90f754f253ee3d9b26a65f21a575e5d936","tid":2074474,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:07:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">裝修師回歸</span>"},{"pid":"4a8aaad5e82c2a852c0c72d1d9daa5efeb1ef5cb","tid":2074474,"uid":193100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"政府個保就業，暫時拎得最多錢嘅係養和，有8595萬；全年蝕7.5億嘅I.T排第二，拎咗4711幾萬；全年蝕近3億嘅TVB拎3274萬；至於利豐三間物流公司夾埋拎2055萬。<br />\n<br />\n留意番，呢分名單係未齊嘅，最終排名有待公佈。<br />\n<br />\n傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ess.gov.hk/pdf/successful_applicant_list_1.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ess.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fsuccessful_applicant_list_1.pdf&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F1EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=07e601c5\" data-auto-link target=